@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

|User Query| as UQ

[LLM Understanding] as LLMU
[Knowledge Retrieval] as KR
[Response Generation] as RG
[Supply Understanding] as SU

rectangle "RAG Pipeline" as RAG {
  [Query\nUnderstanding]
  [Vector\nRetrieval]
  [Knowledge\nRanking]
  [Context\nIntegration]
}

rectangle "Supply Understanding\nwith LLM" as SU2 {
  [Intent\nRecognition]
  [Entity\nUnderstanding]
  [Matching\nOptimization]
  [Explanation\nGeneration]
}

UQ --> LLMU
LLMU --> RAG: Parse Query
RAG --> RG: Retrieve + Context
RG --> SU2: Generate Response
SU2 --> [Supply Matching]

note right of RAG
  Retrieval Augmented
  Generation combines
  LLM with knowledge base
end note

@enduml
